        "answer": "Bowmans Tanzania's official website is https://bowmanslaw.com. Michael Strain is the managing partner. Bowmans provides legal services in Tanzania.\nBowmans Tanzania is a law firm with offices in multiple African countries, specializing in legal services including IP and litigation. It was established in 2017 and has received awards for its practice.\nBowmans is a prominent law firm in Tanzania, specializing in corporate, commercial, and dispute resolution law. It has multiple offices across Africa and is highly regarded for its expertise in complex transactions. Founded in Tanzania, it has a strong reputation for providing high-quality legal services.\nBowmans is a leading law firm in Tanzania, specializing in corporate, commercial, and dispute resolution law. It has multiple offices across Africa and is part of the Lex Mundi network. The firm has won several awards, including Law Firm of the Year in Tanzania.\nBowmans is a leading African law firm with a strong presence in Tanzania, specializing in corporate, commercial, and dispute resolution law. They have multiple offices across Africa and are recognized for their expertise in mergers and acquisitions. Bowmans has received numerous awards, including Law Firm of the Year in Tanzania.",
